examples.en: We keep dogs in the yard to drive off intruders.
They built a 10ft high fence to secure the house against intruders.
The guards have orders to shoot intruders on sight (=shoot them as soon as they see them).
The intruders tied Kurt up and left him.
The dog's barking gave the alarm and the intruders were caught.
He bought a dog with the intention of training it to attack intruders.
